CustomField.description: List of object API names separated by ";" whose attachments and files need to be exported to Amazon S3. If "All", all attachments will be moved to Amazon S3. If empty, no attachments will be moved to Amazon S3.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: List of object API names separated by ";" whose attachments and files need to be exported to Amazon S3. If "All", all attachments will be moved to Amazon S3. If empty, no attachments will be moved to Amazon S3.
CustomField.label: Objects to Export Salesforce Files
